Math-HoltWinters version 0.03
=============================

This module provides implementations of the Holt-Winters (Exponential
Smoothing) methods for time series analysis and forecasting.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module does not require other modules.

